channel.title: Puget Sound Real Estate Careers and Training Video Blog with Gavin Shnieder
channel.description: Our mission at Abode Base is to help others build sustainable wealth through Real Estate. Whether you are a buyer, seller, or investor, our team of professionals can answer any questions you might have about real estate. If you are looking to buy or sell a home, you can get all the information and the latest updates, tips, and tricks from The Abode Base Real Estate, your professional Puget Sound Real Estate Agents.
